{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Potion Shopkeeper is a cozy 3D game where you run a potion shop, craft potions, set prices, and manage customer reactions. Unlock rare ingredients, experiment with recipes, and manage your reputation to attract more customers and grow your shop!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/lucky_luke_happy.png?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/1b87f1bdc8d6f47e6089b6f899a87d40.gif?t=1738254391\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Potion Shopkeeper</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Potion Shopkeeper is an adorable 3D simulation game where you run a cozy potion shop in a charming fantasy world. You'll brew potions, experiment with ingredients, and manage your shop by setting prices and handling customer reactions, balancing relaxation with strategic thinking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/lucky_luke.png?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/0d2fb88a6c34663eda372d68cc9947a2.gif?t=1738254391\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you expand, Fred the vendor helps you unlock rare ingredients for crafting valuable potions. Maintaining a good reputation is crucial, as it affects your shop's popularity. With intuitive controls and simple drag-and-drop mechanics, Potion Shopkeeper offers a creative and immersive resource management experience.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738254391","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738254391","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/855a9dfb8eefa3f8fffcdd0fdc0bf5050e0dc0a0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738254391","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/855a9dfb8eefa3f8fffcdd0fdc0bf5050e0dc0a0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738254391","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Attract happy customers!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/characters.png?t=1738254391\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Potion Shopkeeper is a cozy 3D game where you run a potion shop, craft potions, set prices, and manage customer reactions. Unlock rare ingredients, experiment with recipes, and manage your reputation to attract more customers and grow your shop!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304710/extras/lucky_luke_happy.png?t=1738254391\" /></p><p class=\"